      "span_text": "Until recently, the conventional management had been by bracing the shoulder in internal rotation. [CITATION_1] However, in a prospective multicentre study to evaluate the results of conservative treatment of primary anterior dislocation of the shoulder, Hovelius et al 1 found that bracing in internal rotation did not prevent recurrence after a primary dislocation.",
